data.description: NEW LISTING! Wonderful RANCH Home! Here is your opportunity to build equity in yourself & STOP paying rent! Become a homeowner today! Open kitchen with slider out to large level lot! Appliances stay with home! Oversized garage & shed! Exterior features deck with wonderful views of nature & direct access to Hennepin Canal! Per seller updates include: Updated bathroom, new water heater, & new door. Ring doorbell & cameras staying with the home. Fireplace worked last time seller used but has not used it for a long time so it is not warranted by seller.  Pool stays but not warranted by seller.
